Identify elements in results section12Primary research articles – Discussion (I)
Identify elements in discussion section13Primary research articles – Discussion (II)
Identify elements in discussion section14Review articles – Abstract, introduction, and methods
Identify elements in abstract, introduction, and methods sections15Review articles – Results and discussion
Identify elements in results and discussion sections16How to perform a literature search?17How to proceed when reading a scientific paper/How to read reference
In class practice: doing it efficiently; writing a summary of review paper18Final Examination 

